FleetAsset.name: FleetAsset
FleetAsset.description: Represents the relationship between an asset and the fleet to which it belongs.

AssetId.description: The Asset associated with the Fleet Asset record.

AssetUsage.description: The total usage of an asset such as the number of hours for which a machine runs.

AssetUsageUomId.description: The unit of measure for the total usage of an asset.

EffectiveEndDate.description: The date until when an asset is part of the fleet.

EffectiveStartDate.description: The date from when an asset is part of the fleet.

FleetId.description: The fleet associated with the Fleet Asset record.

LastReferencedDate.description: The most recent date on which a user referenced this record.

LastViewedDate.description: The most recent date on which a user viewed this record.

Name.description: The autopopulated name of a Fleet Asset record.

Status.description: Specifies the status of the asset in the associated fleet.
